       IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
       PROGRAM-ID. ACCOUNT-BALANCE-PROG.

       DATA DIVISION.
       WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
       01  ACCOUNT-BALANCE-VALUE      PIC 9(4)V99 VALUE 1000.00.
       01  DEPOSIT-AMOUNT-VALUE       PIC 9(4)V99 VALUE 250.00.
       01  WITHDRAWAL-AMOUNT-VALUE    PIC 9(4)V99 VALUE 100.00.
       01  AMOUNT-FMT                 PIC Z(4).99.

       PROCEDURE DIVISION.
           MOVE ACCOUNT-BALANCE-VALUE TO AMOUNT-FMT.
           DISPLAY "Initial Balance : " AMOUNT-FMT.

           MOVE DEPOSIT-AMOUNT-VALUE TO AMOUNT-FMT.
           DISPLAY "Deposited       : " AMOUNT-FMT.

           MOVE WITHDRAWAL-AMOUNT-VALUE TO AMOUNT-FMT.
           DISPLAY "Withdrawn       : " AMOUNT-FMT.

           ADD DEPOSIT-AMOUNT-VALUE TO ACCOUNT-BALANCE-VALUE.
           SUBTRACT WITHDRAWAL-AMOUNT-VALUE FROM ACCOUNT-BALANCE-VALUE.
           MOVE ACCOUNT-BALANCE-VALUE TO AMOUNT-FMT.
           DISPLAY "Final Balance   : " AMOUNT-FMT.


           STOP RUN.


